@startuml Search

title POST /search — 의미 기반 벡터 검색 (LCEL)

actor Client
participant "FastAPI\n(search.py)" as API
participant "chain.py\n(LCEL)" as CHAIN
participant "Embedder" as EMB
participant "QdrantStore" as QD
database "SQLite/PG\n(DB)" as DB

Client -> API : POST /search\n{query, top_k?, document_id?}
note right of API
  인증: JWT Bearer 또는
  X-Service-Token (MCP용)
end note
activate API

API -> CHAIN : run_search(db, SearchQuery)
activate CHAIN

note over CHAIN
  **LCEL 파이프라인**
  RunnableParallel(query=passthrough, vector=embed)
    | search
    | enrich
end note

CHAIN -> EMB : embed_query(query.query)
activate EMB
EMB --> CHAIN : vector[float]
deactivate EMB

CHAIN -> QD : search(vector, top_k, document_id?)
activate QD
note right of QD
  document_id 있으면
  payload filter 적용
  (Qdrant payload index 활용)
end note
QD --> CHAIN : list[SearchHit]\n(point_id, score, payload)
deactivate QD

CHAIN -> DB : SELECT Document WHERE id IN (doc_ids)
activate DB
note right of DB
  N+1 방지: 한 번의 IN 쿼리로
  모든 document title 조회
end note
DB --> CHAIN : list[Document]
deactivate DB

CHAIN --> API : list[EnrichedHit]\n(document_id, document_title,\nordinal, score, text, metadata)
deactivate CHAIN

API --> Client : 200 SearchResponse\n{query, hits[]}

deactivate API

@enduml
